item.title: Ruth Richie
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: I have just finished my studies in Early Childhood Education, and I am also the kid's yoga teacher here at Fable. I enjoy cooking,swimming and bike riding in my free time.

item.title: Katie Willmore
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: My name is Katie. I grew up and studied in Canada. This is my second year at Fable and love every minute of it, making the childrens learning experience fun.

item.title: Angelica Watson
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: I hold a degree in Early Childhood Education and an advanced English language certificate. I have been working as a kindergarten teacher since 2002.

item.title: Angela Lynn
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: I have completed a Graduate Diploma in Early Childhood Teaching. I have worked with children aged from six weeks to eight years. This is my second year at Fable.

item.title: Claire Willmore
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: I have just finished my studies in Early Childhood Education, and I am also the kids yoga teacher here at Fable. I enjoy cooking,swimming and bike riding in my free time.

item.title: Linda Moore
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: I hold a degree in Early Childhood Education and an advanced English language certificate. I have been working as a kindergarten teacher since 2002.
